{"id":159427,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/討薪被砍斷筋-群眾燒車抗議/","date":"2011-06-09T04:00:31Z","modified":"2011-12-28T23:38:12Z","title":"討薪被砍斷筋 群眾燒車抗議","content":"<p>廣東潮州潮安縣古巷鎮日前發生一起四川民工討薪致殘的消息，遭老闆挑斷手腳筋脈的18歲工人熊漢江，有終身殘廢之虞，引起當地的四川民工憤怒，連日來在潮州市政府外聚集抗議。6日晚間更有數百人示威抗議，與鎮暴警察爆發嚴重衝突，其後傳出爆炸聲響，據稱現場有1輛商務車被焚、逾40輛車被砸毀。3名嫌疑人已被拘捕到案。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/15bf478e/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E8%A8%8E%E8%96%AA%E8%A2%AB%E7%A0%8D%E6%96%B7%E7%AD%8B+%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE%E7%87%92%E8%BB%8A%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F17180501%2F172011060800207.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E8%A8%8E%E8%96%AA%E8%A2%AB%E7%A0%8D%E6%96%B7%E7%AD%8B+%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE%E7%87%92%E8%BB%8A%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F17180501%2F172011060800207.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104471413267/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/15bf478e/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104471413267/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/15bf478e/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/15bf478e/mf.gif\" /></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> </p>\n<p>\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[18424],"tags":[16304,15396]}